p.k: When the Score creeper traps Unikitty and the gang in his laser tag arena the gang must defeat the house team or be imprisoned forever. / Unikitty and gang have ordered some delicious Thai food for dinner. Unfortunately the wait for the delivery is proving too much, time itself seems to have slowed down. / Unikitty's installed Bad Vibe detectors in the castle. / Sadness levels have hit an all-time low in Frowntown. In an attempt to cheer up the citizens, Unikitty and the gang want to release a rainbow over the town. / When Toast disappears from Unikitty's party she leads a search to find him and expose the toast-napper.
